NAME
    Role::TinyCommons::TermAttr::Size - Determine the sane terminal size
    (width, height)

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.003 of
    Role::TinyCommons::TermAttr::Size (from Perl distribution
    Role-TinyCommons-TermAttr-Size), released on 2020-06-06.

DESCRIPTION
    Uses Term::App::Util::Size as backend.

PROVIDED METHODS
  termattr_height
  termattr_width
HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Role-TinyCommons-TermAttr-Size>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-Role-TinyCommons-TermAttr-Size>.

